contentrichtext.text: '''Rhee''' may refer to: * A common Korean surname, [[Lee (Korean name)]], which is also commonly transliterated as Rhee or Yi * Several people bearing the Korean surname, as noted at [[List of people with the Korean family name Lee]] * A village in the Netherlands named [[Rhee (Drenthe)]] ==People with the surname Rhee== * [[Margaret Rhee]], American feminist poet * [[Michelle Rhee]], American educator and former Chancellor of the District of Columbia school system * [[Peter M. Rhee]], American physician and US Navy veteran * [[Phillip Rhee]], Korean-American actor and martial-arts master * [[Syngman Rhee]], South Korean President {{disambig}}
